Package: W4MRUtils
Title: Utils List for W4M - Workflow for Metabolomics
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c( person("Lain", "Pavot", "", "lain.pavot@inrae.fr", role =
        c("aut", "cre")), person("Melanie", "Petera", "",
        "melanie.petera@inrae.fr", role = c("aut")))
Description: Provides a set of utility function to prevent the spread
        of utilities script in W4M (Workflow4Metabolomics) scripts, and
        centralize them in a single package. Some are meant to be
        replaced by real packages in a near future, like the
        parse_args() function: it is here only to prepare the ground
        for more global changes in W4M scripts and tools.
